<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>SmartBasket</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/logo" href="https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/ai-robot-shopping-cart-icon-ecommerce-retail-store-marketplace-vector-illustration-446380951.jpg" /> 
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="shell">
      <nav class="nav">
        <a class="brand" href="/">
          <span class="brand-mark">DL</span>
          <span><bold>DealLens AI</bold></span>
        </a>
        <div class="nav-actions">
          <a class="back-link" href="#analyze">Analyze</a>
          <a class="back-link" href="#demo">Demo response</a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <section class="hero landing-hero">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <h2 class="" style="font-family: cursive;font-weight: semi-bold;"><bold>SmartBasket</bold></h2>
          <h1 class="split-heading" data-split-heading>
            <span>Find the lowest</span>
            <span>product price across</span>
            <span>trusted stores.</span>
          </h1>
          <p>
            Paste a product URL or product name. DealLens scans product details, searches matching listings, and returns a structured buying report with platform, price, source URL, and checkout checks.
          </p>

          <form id="analyze" class="search-panel" action="/analyze" method="POST" data-loading-form>
            <label for="productUrl">Product link or name</label>
            <div class="input-row">
              <input
                id="productUrl"
                name="productUrl"
                type="text"
                placeholder="Paste Amazon/Flipkart URL or type wireless headphones"
                autocomplete="off"
                required
              />
              <button type="submit" data-loading-button>Analyze</button>
            </div>
            <div class="quick-links">
              <span>Amazon</span>
              <span>Flipkart</span>
              <span>Myntra</span>
              <span>Croma</span>
              <span>Shows direct seller URLs</span>
            </div>
            <% if (error) { %>
              <p class="error"><%= error %></p>
            <% } %>
          </form>
        </div>

        <aside class="media-stage" aria-label="Shopping analysis preview">
          <video
            class="hero-image" autoplay muted loop playsinline
            poster="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/31/amazonservices/Blog/eCommerce_Platform.png"
            alt="Online shopping checkout on a laptop">
            <source src="upload/istockphoto-2182642770-640_adpp_is.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>

          <video class="hero-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607082349566-187342175e2f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80">
            <source src="/upload/istockphoto-1492291415-640_adpp_is.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <svg class="analysis-svg" viewBox="0 0 420 230" role="img" aria-label="AI compares prices from multiple stores">
            <rect x="24" y="24" width="372" height="182" rx="22" fill="#ffffff" />
            <path d="M68 76h96M68 114h190M68 152h150" stroke="#000000" stroke-width="14" stroke-linecap="round" />
            <path d="M296 68l34 34 56-62" fill="none" stroke="#000000" stroke-width="16" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            <circle cx="326" cy="150" r="36" fill="#000000" />
            <path d="M308 151l14 14 28-34" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
          <div class="floating-report">
            <span>Lowest platform</span>
            <strong>AI verified seller URL</strong>
            <small>Structured answer after scan</small>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section class="trust-row" aria-label="DealLens capabilities">
        <div>
          <strong>Lowest price</strong>
          <span>Ranks current visible prices from matching product pages.</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong>Product scan</strong>
          <span>Reads available title, image, description, and price from the link.</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong>Visit links</strong>
          <span>Every offer includes a URL so shoppers can verify the seller.</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="landing-band">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
          <h2>From pasted link to buying decision in one clean report.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="steps-grid">
          <article>
            <span>01</span>
            <strong>Read product detail</strong>
            <p>Extracts title, image, description, visible price, and source store from the submitted product page.</p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <span>02</span>
            <strong>Search matching sellers</strong>
            <p>Uses AI web search to compare likely same-product listings across credible ecommerce platforms.</p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <span>03</span>
            <strong>Return structured answer</strong>
            <p>Shows lowest platform, visible price, confidence, visit URL, and checkout checks in a scannable format.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="demo" class="response-preview">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div>
            <span class="eyebrow">Response format</span>
            <h2>Clear enough to act on.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>The analysis page is organized around the decision shoppers need: where to buy, why, and what to verify.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="demo-response">
          <div>
            <span>Best price</span>
            <strong>Platform + live price</strong>
            <small>Direct product URL included</small>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>AI recommendation</span>
            <strong>Buy / wait / verify</strong>
            <small>Reasons and checkout checks</small>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>Marketplace ranking</span>
            <strong>Lowest to highest</strong>
            <small>Visual bars and seller cards</small>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <div class="loading-screen" data-loading-screen aria-live="polite" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="loading-card">
        <div class="loader-ring" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Analyzing deal</span>
        <h2>Scanning product and finding live offers</h2>
        <p>DealLens is checking the submitted page, searching matching seller listings, and preparing a structured AI recommendation.</p>
        <div class="loading-steps">
          <span>Reading product details</span>
          <span>Comparing prices</span>
          <span>Structuring AI advice</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/gsap.min.js" defer></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js" defer></script>
    <script src="/app.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
